OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry
OL,6,Fovernight with variable amounts of
OL,7,Fcloud and lengthy clear spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping. An early dip in
OL,9,Ftemperatures before cloudier skies and
OL,10,Fpatchy rain arrives across the region
OL,11,Ftowards dawn. Mostly light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FCloudy with patchy rain
OL,14,Facross the region from early morning.
OL,15,FSoon turning brighter with sunny
OL,16,Fspells developing from the north.
OL,17,FBecoming increasingly blustery into
OL,18,Fthe afternoon with scattered showers
OL,19,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
