OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FBlustery with sunny spells and heavy
OL,7,Fshowers on both Wednesday and
OL,8,FThursday. More settled on Friday with
OL,9,Fdrier and brighter conditions.
OL,10,FRemaining chilly, with a risk of frost.
